Apple's realistic lighting and glossy shading give the woman's form a sense of fluidity and energy, while the ball has a satisfyingly round, tactile appearance. This emoji embodies playfulness, athleticism, and joyous activity, perfect for conveying enthusiasm and fun in messages.
